FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Got questions? We've got answers. Here's what our foodies want to know!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app connects food lovers with local restaurants, recipes, and culinary experiences. Simply browse, select, and enjoy!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Is the app free to use?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Yes, the basic version of our app is completely free. We also offer a premium version with additional features for a small monthly fee.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I order food delivery through the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Absolutely! We partner with local restaurants to offer a wide variety of cuisine options for delivery right to your doorstep.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Are there vegetarian and vegan options available?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Of course! We cater to all dietary preferences and restrictions, including vegetarian, vegan, gluten-free, and more.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How can I share my food experiences on the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: You can easily share photos, reviews, and recommendations with our community. Just snap a pic, write your thoughts, and post!
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Food App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the food delivery feature work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our food delivery feature connects you with local restaurants and delivery services. Simply browse menus, place your order, and track its progress in real-time. We ensure your meal arrives fresh and on time.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Can I find recipes and cooking tips in the app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Absolutely! Our app includes a vast collection of recipes, cooking tutorials, and expert tips. Whether you're a beginner or a seasoned chef, you'll find inspiration and guidance for your next culinary creation.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Is there a meal planning feature available?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Yes, we offer a comprehensive meal planning tool. You can create weekly menus, generate shopping lists, and even sync with your calendar. Our app makes it easy to plan balanced, delicious meals for you and your family.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: How can I discover new restaurants in my area?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Our app features a local restaurant discovery section where you can explore eateries near you. Browse user reviews, view menus, and even make reservations directly through the app. It's your gateway to new culinary experiences in your neighborhood.
